{"tid":1254874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十八區勇武有無得諗","createTime":"2019-06-24T09:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T12:31:08.000Z","uid":114483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5da36e7da3cd7860c8a273329352cf30df70ab","tid":1254874,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:49:27.000Z","msg":"首先一樣野，唔好再互屌，26要出。<br />\n<br />\n依家十八區都有好多廢老街站，有無可能各區既巴打都聚集一齊，邊到有街站，就去圍佢地，企定定阻人睇都好。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得，可以係唔同地區既地標or 社區會堂聚集先，收到風邊到有站就去周邊到，愈多人就愈好，兩百萬人唔係做呢啲都唔敢呀。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家ok 既就行動，同埋希望文宣都可以做下野"},{"pid":"f9d2c950d385ccecae4d1a51543522d94ae00596","tid":1254874,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"依幾日可以做既係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n612文宣嘅成功大家有目共睹<br />\n我地要做多一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面嘅圖應該係大家finalized 嘅 version<br />\n三件事<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.626日頭請願</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.夜晚民陣集會</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3.627接力搞律政司</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依三張一定要 po上ig story先</span></span>，fb其次。<br />\nIg story最好每日 po一次，加埋 caption<br />\nCaption :<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">一定要去/唔好等到七一/番工嘅咪放工去/唔去都幫手share</span></span><br />\n<br />\n進階版！<br />\n街站！！！痴街招！！！放映會派<br />\n如果可以就行多一步<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>勇武兄弟抖抖，626需要你地</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔夠人講乜都冇用，唔夠人就輸</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WK7XjEf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWK7XjEf.jpg&h=abb463aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kv4KHay.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKv4KHay.jpg&h=d6021045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07BpHaE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07BpHaE.jpg&h=01107ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74o7GS5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74o7GS5.png&h=80fb449e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4OPaMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4OPaMr.jpg&h=10fc019e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12ff4ba101b1ebb8408e6588c8e8a683f349bb07","tid":1254874,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"諗你老母啦諗<br />\n<br />\n安坐家中弱智ive仔鍵盤司令官<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64247e2b2e733eee65f4ac799a81294a61887e4","tid":1254874,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12ff4ba101b1ebb8408e6588c8e8a683f349bb07","tid":1254874,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"諗你老母啦諗<br />\n<br />\n安坐家中弱智ive仔鍵盤司令官<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"點話點好啦，分化撚，過左數未？"},{"pid":"bae456701244329db0ef2c7e1caa4bf828d2284d","tid":1254874,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"發夢直接拆場打人<br />\n有無得諗？"},{"pid":"18805b4a4229128b9b1ea8c187e8f484b365fa4a","tid":1254874,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faf55044692346b2484c744a5